					-
						-
							Part 1: Book 6: Chapter 1: Decade 1: Verse 1
						-
							-
								The Gods have come to Indu well-descended, beautified with milk,
								the active crusher of the foe.
							-
						-
							Part 1: Book 6: Chapter 1: Decade 1: Verse 2
						-
							-
